metadata.name: Mountain View Distant Pink
metadata.description:
The complexities of the human psyche and the effect of our environment can literally colour the way we view things. This series of paintings explores these complexities using the visual elements of colour and shape only. A kaleidoscope of elements creating a kaleidoscope of views. Only you have the power to choose your view.  
2953 x2953 px
Acrylic on canvas
